00:00:06.497 --> 00:00:08.734
Today we will make Sabudana (sago pearls) kheer.

00:00:08.896 --> 00:00:12.205
Sabudana kheer can also be served during vrat.

00:00:12.446 --> 00:00:18.014
Let’s see what all ingredients are required for making sabudana kheer.

00:00:18.325 --> 00:00:21.191
Milk - 1 liter (or 5 cups)

00:00:21.615 --> 00:00:28.533
Sago pearls - ¾ cup (soaked for ½ hour)

00:00:29.044 --> 00:00:30.567
Sugar - ½ cup

00:00:31.523 --> 00:00:33.365
Cashew nuts - 1 tbsp

00:00:33.677 --> 00:00:35.613
Raisins - 1 tbsp

00:00:35.767 --> 00:00:37.338
Green cardamom - 4-5

00:00:37.729 --> 00:00:39.563
Pistachios - 6-7

00:00:40.143 --> 00:00:41.778
Let’s start with the procedure of making kheer.

00:00:42.491 --> 00:00:45.522
Place milk on flame for heating.

00:00:46.253 --> 00:00:52.938
When milk starts boiling, add sago pearls into it.

00:00:53.366 --> 00:00:55.787
When milk starts boiling, add sago pearls into it.

00:00:55.916 --> 00:01:06.867
If we use big sago pearls then soak them for 6 hours before bringing in use.

00:01:13.797 --> 00:01:16.257
Cut dry fruits.

00:01:20.019 --> 00:01:23.035
Make 5-6 pieces of one cashew nut.

00:01:28.814 --> 00:01:35.081
Finely chop pistachios as they will be used for garnishing the kheer.

00:01:38.969 --> 00:01:43.446
Milk has started boiling; now mix sago pearls into it.

00:01:47.533 --> 00:01:54.680
After adding sago pearls keep stirring the milk constantly as it may coagulate.

00:01:54.998 --> 00:02:01.673
Keep stirring until it starts boiling again.

00:02:06.245 --> 00:02:12.646
Bring the flame to medium for cooking kheer.

00:02:13.653 --> 00:02:19.521
Bring the flame to medium for cooking kheer.

00:02:25.947 --> 00:02:33.996
Add raisins and cashew nuts as well.

00:02:37.241 --> 00:02:41.384
Cook on medium flame.

00:02:41.524 --> 00:02:46.325
Stir after every 2 minutes else milk will get burn.

00:03:02.551 --> 00:03:05.212
Sago pearls have become soft.

00:03:07.581 --> 00:03:09.795
Now add sugar in the kheer.

00:03:25.396 --> 00:03:30.401
Also add cardamom powder and turn off the gas.

00:03:34.651 --> 00:03:36.770
Sabudana kheer is ready.

00:03:41.078 --> 00:03:44.930
Garnish with pistachios.

00:03:48.086 --> 00:03:51.096
Appetizing sabudana kheer is ready.

00:03:51.406 --> 00:03:57.084
Prepare sabudana kheer during vrat or whenever you like eating.

